title: Technological Implant
comment: The Ethics of Having an implant discussed

title: Energy Efficient
comment: Repairs itself and charges itself, no need to worry about running out of charge

title: Decomposes when not wanted
comment: No need to worry about having to have it physically removed

title: Military - Making killing more likely
comment: Could make soldiers more dangerous and unstable

title: Helps Sleep (Less Sleep needed)
comment: Can allow people to be more productive

title: Lower Risk of Fatigue Accidents
comment: Accidents from sleep deprivation can be reduced, E.g. car accidents

title: Social Divide/Class Divide
comment: Could create a divide between different classes for people who have and people who dont have the implant

title: Privacy
comment: People may be worried of having information they dont want to be leaked, leaked to the outside world

title: Hackers
comment: Due to the infancy of the tech, it could be prone to hacks

title: Unknown Health Factors
comment: Due to the early Technology we don't know of any health related factors of having it inside your head

title: Price
comment: Linked with the social divide, some people may not be able to afford
